    Descubre todas las comunidades que forman parte de la organizaci√≥n del evento
  </p>
  <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-around gap-5">
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adaindatabo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <Image
        src={Ada}
        alt="Ada In Data Logo"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mb-5 w-20"
      />
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/GDGCochabamba " target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <Image
        src={GDGCocha}
        alt="GDG Cochabamba logo"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mb-5 w-28 sm:w-40"
      />
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/MujeresTICsBO" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <Image
        src={MujeresTics}
        alt="Mujeres Tics logo"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mb-5 w-24"
      />
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/notionbolivia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <Image
        src={Notion}
        alt="Notion logo"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mb-5 w-24"
      />
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pyladiescbba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
